Package com.whirvis.jraknet.protocol

The packets and extra components required for communication between both the server and the client to be possible.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Failable
    Packets that extend this class indicate that they have a possibility of failing to encode or decode.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectionType
    Used to signify which implementation of the RakNet protocol is being used by a connection.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Reliability
    Represents a RakNet reliability.
